STATE EX REL. FETHEROLF
v.
SHAW 2018-1752 Supreme Court of Ohio. February 13, 2019

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

O'Connor, C.J., and Kennedy, French, Fischer, DeWine, Donnelly, and Stewart, JJ., concur.

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

In Prohibition. On respondents' motion to dismiss. Motion granted. Cause dismissed. Relator's motion in response to the state's motion to dismiss denied as moot.
